      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHIAN MIKEY (1) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in three starts, including two wins. Scored by 1.5 lengths last time (22.04) in a Grade 5 over 380m at this track. Rates a leading player. FARMOR AGAIN (4) goes very well this trip starting eight times for four wins and three minors. Placed last time (24.13) at Rockhampton in a Grade 4, finishing third and beaten 3 lengths. Can feature in the finish. STARRY RAYMAR (2) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (22.04) at this track. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Should be about the money. FEDERAL HARRY (3) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
